        "<strong>20%:</strong> Excellent service",
        "<strong>25%+:</strong> Exceptional service"
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "When to Tip",
      "type": "list",
      "content": [
        "<strong>Restaurants:</strong> 15-20% of bill before tax",
        "<strong>Bars:</strong> $1-2 per drink or 15-20% of tab",
